rows.label: tlk43420341_01_msg0003
rows.name:
Vandham's favorite meal is an Armu
T-Bone Steak.

rows.label: tlk43420341_01_msg0004
rows.name:
Maybe you just eat anything on hand
when you're out adventuring...

rows.label: tlk43420341_01_msg0005
rows.name:
but eating something you like or love
gives you a much bigger effect.

rows.label: tlk43420341_01_msg0006
rows.name:
It also helps build Trust with
your Blade.

rows.label: tlk43420341_01_msg0007
rows.name:
It's important to check your allies'
preferences when you're off
adventuring.
